        <mxCell id="s5_lambda" value="" style="sketch=0;outlineConnect=0;fontColor=#232F3E;gradientColor=none;fillColor=#ED7100;strokeColor=#ffffff;dashed=0;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;align=center;html=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;aspect=fixed;shape=mxgraph.aws4.resourceIcon;resIcon=mxgraph.aws4.lambda;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1420" y="555" width="50" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s5_text" value="• EventBridge / SNS / SQS で完全疎結合&#10;• イベントソーシング + CQRS 採用可&#10;• 新機能追加はルール追加のみ — 既存影響 0&#10;• Observability: X-Ray / CloudWatch Logs Insights&#10;• IaC (SAM / CDK) + CI/CD で デプロイ自動化" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontColor=#232F3E;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1135" y="615" width="390" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- Arrows between stages -->
        <mxCell id="s_arr1" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#7AA116;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="s1_box" target="s2_box">
